<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Payment Link for Your Quote - Genfix</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #007bff; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .content { background: #fff; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 8px; }
    .payment-box { background: #e7f3ff; border: 2px solid #007bff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; text-align: center; }
    .price { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #007bff; }
    .btn-pay { display: inline-block; background: #007bff; color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .secure { background: #d4edda; border: 1px solid #c3e6cb; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸ’³ Payment Link Ready</h1>
      <p>Complete your booking securely</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p><%= @greeting %>,</p>

      <p>Thank you for approving your quote! Your payment link is ready.</p>

      <div class="payment-box">
        <h2>Payment Due</h2>
        <div class="price">$<%= number_with_precision(@quote_request.quote_price, precision: 2) %></div>
        <p>for <%= @quote_request.equipment_type %></p>

        <a href="<%= @payment_url %>" class="btn-pay">ðŸ”’ Pay Now Securely</a>
      </div>

      <div class="secure">
        <strong>ðŸ”’ Secure Payment</strong><br>
        Your payment is processed securely through Stripe with 256-bit SSL encryption.
        We never store your card details.
      </div>

      <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0;">
        <h3>What happens after payment?</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>You'll receive a confirmation email with delivery details</li>
          <li>Our team will contact you to schedule delivery</li>
          <li>Licensed electrician will deliver and install your equipment</li>
          <li>24/7 support available throughout your rental period</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <p><strong>Need to make changes?</strong> Call us on <strong>0412 345 678</strong> before completing payment.</p>

      <p>This payment link expires in 7 days for security reasons.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>
      The Genfix Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>